Executive: Achcha.

Executive: Hmm hmm hmm.
Customer: Agar koi customer ya to koi other person hamara catalog hamara profile show karta hai to wo hume dikhta hai na to hume malum padta hai ki hamara catalog koi search kar raha hai to to hamara IndiaMART pe hamara profile bhi dikhta hai matlab agar nahi dikh raha hai to to hi wo nahi show hoga na.
Executive: Hmm hmm hmm hmm.

Customer: Chalega chalega.
Executive: Thik hai baki request hai sir abhi main call katne ke baad aap ticket close karungi feedback mera please yes de dijiyega baki jo bhi aapka problem hai sab main video call pe solve karaungi thik hai aur abhi main hai na aapko ek ek second aur ruko aap ye aur batao aapko jo leads aap le rahe ho leads mein kuch business wagera mil raha hai?
Customer: Nahi mil raha nahi mil raha dekho main khali isliye purchase kar raha hu kyunki na apna hum active reh sake isliye main purchase kar raha hu lekin Mumbai ki bahut kam mil rahi hai fir bhi jabse call kiya aap aapko to tabse thoda bahut mujhe business dekhne ko mila hai barabar aisa nahi hai ke nahi hua hai.
Executive: Hmm hmm hmm.
Executive: Thik hai no problem to main use kya bolte hain isko thik kar deti hu ek minute call pe rahiyega please hai na aur ek cheez aur batao sir mujhe aap ye to ek calling ka issue hai aapka dusra aapka jo issue hai wo hai aapka kya issue bataya dusra aapne aapko catalog view ke options nahi.
Customer: Nahi dusra main main aapko ek kaam karo na main thoda kaam mein hu.
Executive: Almost kitne minute pe daal.
Customer: Main kya bol raha hu minute nahi hote hain.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan ji bataiye.
Customer: Main kya bol raha hu main thoda kaam mein hu to aap na mujhe aapke mein aap ye ticket aap close karo.
Executive: Thik hai thik hai main karti hu ticket close kar rahi hu lekin please iska feedback pe yes kar dijiyega I am requesting please request.
Customer: Chalega chalega thik hai.
Executive: Thik hai thik hai sir.

- Executive clarified catalog view option is removed.

- Executive will solve the problem on video call.

- Customer to provide positive feedback.
